---
import { BRAND } from "@/config/brand";
import Base from "@/layouts/Base.astro";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
const pageTitle = `About ${BRAND.name}`;
const pageMetaTitle = `About ${BRAND.name}`;
const pageDescription = `${BRAND.name} â€” ${BRAND.tagline}`;
---

<Base
  title={pageTitle}
  meta_title={pageMetaTitle}
  description={pageDescription}
>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-24 max-w-4xl">
    <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-8">{pageTitle}</h1>

    <div class="mb-12">
      <Image
        src="/images/banner-art.webp"
        alt="Financial Blog Template banner"
        width={1200}
        height={600}
        class="w-full rounded-xl object-cover shadow-md"
      />
    </div>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <p class="text-lg mb-6">
        At {BRAND.name}, we believe that smart financial decisions shouldn't be
        complicated, expensive, or biased.
      </p>

      <p class="mb-6">
        We understand that Gen-Z and Millennials face unique financial
        challenges in today's economy - from student loans and gig work to
        rising costs and uncertain futures. That's why we've created a space
        where you can get honest, unbiased financial guidance without the sales
        pitches or hidden agendas.
      </p>

      <p class="mb-6">
        Our mission is simple: to provide clear, actionable financial advice
        that empowers you to make confident money decisions, regardless of where
        you are in your financial journey.
      </p>

      <p class="mb-6">
        What makes us different? We don't earn commissions from credit card
        companies, and we don't try to sell you products. We're here to give you
        the real scoop on financial tools and strategies that actually work for
        people like you.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Our Commitment to You</h2>

      <ul class="space-y-6">
        <li class="flex gap-4">
          <span class="text-2xl">ðŸŽ¯</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-xl mb-2">100% Unbiased Guidance</h3>
            <p>
              We don't accept affiliate payments or commissions from financial
              companies. Our recommendations are based solely on what's best for
              you, not what pays us the most.
            </p>
          </div>
        </li>

        <li class="flex gap-4">
          <span class="text-2xl">ðŸ†“</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-xl mb-2">Always Free Access</h3>
            <p>
              Quality financial guidance shouldn't cost money. All our content,
              tools, and resources are completely free - no paywalls, no premium
              tiers, no catch.
            </p>
          </div>
        </li>

        <li class="flex gap-4">
          <span class="text-2xl">ðŸ“±</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-xl mb-2">Modern Money Reality</h3>
            <p>
              Our content is tailored for the financial realities of Gen-Z and
              Millennials - from side hustles and student debt to modern
              spending habits and digital banking.
            </p>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-6">What We Cover</h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-light p-6 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-xl mb-3 text-primary">Credit Cards</h3>
          <p>
            Honest reviews and comparisons of credit cards without the affiliate
            bias. We help you find cards that actually match your spending and
            financial goals.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-light p-6 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-xl mb-3 text-primary">Budgeting</h3>
          <p>
            Practical budgeting strategies that work with modern lifestyles. No
            shame, no judgment - just real advice for real people.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-light p-6 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-xl mb-3 text-primary">
            Financial Wellness
          </h3>
          <p>
            Building emergency funds, understanding investing basics, and
            planning for major life events - all explained in plain English.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-light p-6 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-xl mb-3 text-primary">Money Mindset</h3>
          <p>
            Addressing the emotional and psychological aspects of money
            management that traditional finance advice often ignores.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-6">
        Built by Millennials, for the Next Generation
      </h2>

      <p class="mb-6">
        {BRAND.name} was created by people who understand the unique financial challenges
        facing younger generations. We've lived through economic uncertainty, dealt
        with student loans, navigated the gig economy, and experienced the frustration
        of getting financial advice that doesn't match our reality.
      </p>

      <p class="mb-6">
        That's why our content speaks your language and addresses the real
        financial situations you face - from managing irregular income to making
        sense of all the credit card offers flooding your mailbox.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section id="our-promise" class="mb-12 bg-primary/10 p-8 rounded-xl">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Our Promise</h2>

      <div>
        <p class="text-lg mb-4">
          We promise to always put your financial well-being first.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4">
          No hidden agendas, no sales pitches, no complicated jargon - just
          honest, practical advice to help you build a better financial future.
        </p>
        <p class="font-semibold text-primary">Built by TopNetworks Inc.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Ready to Get Started?</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">
        Explore our unbiased financial guides and start making smarter money
        decisions today.
      </p>
      <a href="/blog" class="btn btn-primary"> Browse Our Financial Guides </a>
    </section>
  </div>
</Base>
